research/history/round_summaries/round_0037.json:27:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{r=1..R} \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + \u03a3_{j\u2208T(x)} \u03b3_j(x) c_j\u3002\u8fd9\u91cc U={u_r} \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{B_e} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0cC={c_j} \u662f\u9759\u6001 residual \u8865\u507f\u5e93\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u5148\u8ba1\u7b97 trunk \u7cfb\u6570 \u03b2_r(x)\uff0c\u518d\u7528\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u62e9\u5355\u4e2a expert \u5b50\u5e93 e(x) \u5e76\u5728\u5176\u5185\u505a\u5c40\u90e8 sparse \u9009\u62e9\uff0c\u6700\u540e\u5bf9\u5269\u4f59\u6b8b\u5dee\u518d\u505a\u4e00\u6b21\u5c0f\u9884\u7b97 sparse \u8865\u507f\u3002\u56e0\u6b64\u5b83\u4ecd\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u6d41\u6c34\u7ebf\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u5728\u4e0e r27 \u76f8\u540c\u7684 EF=1\u3001K=192 recipe \u4e0b\uff0c\u628a `expert_topk` \u5347\u7ea7\u4e3a `lowrank + expert + residual` \u4e09\u6bb5\u5f0f\u7ed3\u6784\uff0c\u80fd\u56de\u7b54\u2018\u4ec5\u6709 lowrank+expert \u4ecd\u4e0d\u8db3\u65f6\uff0c\u52a0\u5165\u7b2c\u4e8c\u6bb5 residual \u4fee\u6b63\u662f\u5426\u4f1a\u5f62\u6210\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u6027 Pareto \u6bb5\u2019\u8fd9\u4e2a\u5f53\u524d\u66f4\u5173\u952e\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0037.json:28:    "summary": "\u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u4e0a\u505a\u7b2c\u4e09\u4e2a\u90bb\u57df\u626b\u70b9\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u8fdb\u5165\u4e0b\u4e00\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff1a\u5b9e\u73b0\u6700\u5c0f\u53ef\u8fd0\u884c\u7684 `lowrank_expert_residual` \u539f\u578b\u3002\u4ee5 r27 \u7684 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` \u4e3a matched baseline\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\uff0c\u5148\u9a8c\u8bc1\u4e09\u6bb5\u5f0f\u7ed3\u6784\u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0037.json:48:      "\u672c\u8f6e\u8981\u56de\u7b54\u7684\u662f\u4e09\u6bb5\u5f0f `lowrank + expert + residual` \u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u518d\u95ee\u4e00\u6b21 `expert_topk` \u6216 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u7684 K \u8f74\u659c\u7387\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0037.json:53:      "\u5982\u679c `lowrank_expert_residual` \u9996\u8f6e\u80fd\u7a33\u5b9a\u8bad\u7ec3\u4e14 FVU \u660e\u663e\u4f18\u4e8e `expert_topk K=192`\uff0c\u4e0b\u4e00\u8f6e\u4fdd\u6301 family \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `STAGE1_RATIO`\uff0c\u9a8c\u8bc1 expert \u6bb5\u4e0e residual \u6bb5\u7684\u9884\u7b97\u5206\u914d\u662f\u5426\u662f\u4e3b\u8981\u63a7\u5236\u65cb\u94ae\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0037.json:91:    "ARCHITECTURE": "expert_topk",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0057.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":56,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_topk"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(x-t(x)) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。在线侧仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判定为扩展兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r56 仅切到 `lowrank_expert_topk`，在保持 `K=128`、`TRUNK_RANK=16`、`NUM_EXPERTS=16` 不变的前提下移除全局 residual cleanup，可以直接回答当前低成本收益究竟主要来自 `lowrank + expert` 本体，还是来自第三段 residual 补偿；如果前者成立，则该 family 应在约 0.40x total_cost 下保持接近 r56 的 FVU，并形成更靠左的新 Pareto 段。","summary":"当前不继续细扫 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 K/ratio，而是做一次高信息量的 matched 结构对照。相对 r56 只改 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，继承已验证有效的低成本 recipe `K=128, TRUNK_RANK=16, NUM_EXPERTS=16`，直接测试在 true sparse-capacity 模式下，`lowrank + expert` 是否已经足够，还是必须依赖 residual cleanup 才能维持当前质量。按当前 cost proxy 估算，该点约为 encoder 0.26x、deployment 0.14x、total 0.40x，处于当前最需要补强的低成本带。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r56 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这不是 old-family 的局部打磨，而是对高优先级未充分验证方向 `lowrank + expert` 做一次真正公平的 matched test；相比继续压 `K` 或 `TRUNK_RANK`，这轮能更清晰地回答三段式结构里 residual 分支是否必要。主要风险是 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在去掉 residual cleanup 后可能明显退化；但无论结果正负，结构信息增量都很高，而且成本位置更贴近当前 <0.5x 主战场。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式是静态 trunk 库加单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","相对 r56 的 matched 对照可以把问题压缩为一个核心判断：当前 0.46x / 0.1113 的收益，究竟主要来自 `lowrank + expert`，还是来自附加的 residual cleanup。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=128 TRUNK_RANK=16 NUM_EXPERTS=16` 的 total_cost 约为 0.40x，明显低于 r56 的 0.46x，也低于当前 <0.5x 带的大多数结构点。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在约 0.40x 成本下仍接近 r56 的 FVU，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=160` 或 `TRUNK_RANK=32`，扩展这条 `lowrank + expert` 低成本前沿。","如果该 family 明显弱于 r56，则可较清晰地判定当前 target 上 residual cleanup 是必要组成，后续应把预算继续投向 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的更优 `K/TRUNK_RANK/STAGE1_RATIO` 组合。","如果该点虽弱于 r56 但仍明显优于 `expert_topk K=192`，则说明 low-rank trunk 本身已经有价值，后续可在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上继续做少量低成本配方压缩，而不必急于放弃这条方向。"]}
