research/history/logs/agent_action_0042.json:3:  "hypothesis": "最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r。也就是先用静态 low-rank trunk 向量库 U={u_r} 重构平滑主干，再对残差用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 B_e={b_{e,i}} 并做局部 sparse 修正；因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路。兼容性判断：`lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容。主假设是：相对 r27 的纯 `expert_topk`，加入轻量 low-rank trunk 后，能显著改善重构质量，并回答 `lowrank + expert` 这条高优先级结构线是否值得继续，即使首点落在中成本带也有信息价值。",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0042.json:4:  "summary": "不回到 plain selector 邻域微调，也不继续对未知结果的 `two_stage_residual_expert` 做预设调参。本轮以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 到 `lowrank_expert_topk`，先拿到 `lowrank + expert` 这条结构线在当前 target 上的首个真实训练点。",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0042.json:7:  "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0042.json:9:  "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r27 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。当前阶段的核心问题是结构扩展，而 `lowrank + expert` 仍是明确列出的高优先级未充分验证方向；用 `expert_topk` 做 matched baseline 归因最干净。该方案的 router 很轻、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1、最终形式仍是静态向量库上的有限加权和，符合 LUTurbo 兼容性要求。虽然首点预计更像中成本质量锚点而非极低成本点，但这仍符合当前允许保留少量 >0.5x 结构对照的策略。",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0042.json:14:      "value": "lowrank_expert_topk"
research/history/logs/agent_action_0042.json:19:    "`lowrank_expert_topk` 的导出形式是静态 low-rank trunk 库加单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0042.json:24:    "如果 `lowrank_expert_topk` 首点明显优于 r27 `expert_topk`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK` 向低成本方向压缩，测试是否能形成新的 Pareto 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0115.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0115.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_shared(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E(x)} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}\u3002\u5176\u4e2d shared \u5b50\u5e93 B^sh \u4e0e routed expert \u5b50\u5e93 {B_e} \u90fd\u662f\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ea\u505a\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u62e9\u5c11\u91cf routed experts\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u6267\u884c shared \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + routed \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u8fd9\u7c7b batch/sample-coupled family \u7ee7\u7eed\u660e\u786e\u6392\u9664\u3002r113 \u5df2\u5728 `K=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64` \u4e0b\u5f62\u6210\u7ea6 0.27x / FVU 0.1350 \u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u524d\u6cbf\u70b9\uff0c\u800c r114 \u8bc1\u660e\u628a `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` \u964d\u5230 1 \u4f1a\u660e\u663e\u4f24\u5bb3\u8d28\u91cf\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d shared+routed \u7684\u6536\u76ca\u786e\u5b9e\u4f9d\u8d56\u53cc routed experts\u3002\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\uff1a\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` \u4e0e `K=64` \u4e0d\u53d8\u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u628a `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` \u4ece 256 \u7f29\u5230 224\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u628a selection cost \u4ece\u7ea6 0.20x \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 0.18x\u3001total_cost \u4ece\u7ea6 0.27x \u5de6\u79fb\u5230\u7ea6 0.24x\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u4ecd\u663e\u8457\u4f18\u4e8e\u65e7\u4f4e\u6210\u672c anchor `expert_topk K=128` \u7684 FVU 0.3149\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u524d\u6cbf\u7684\u4e0b\u4e00\u6b65\u66f4\u8be5\u538b\u6bcf-expert \u5bbd\u5ea6\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u538b active experts\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0115.json:20:    "summary": "\u4ee5 r113 \u4e3a reference\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `shared_routed_expert_topk`\u3001`K=64`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64` \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5728\u5df2\u77e5\u53cc routed experts \u5fc5\u8981\u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0cshared+routed \u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u524d\u6cbf\u662f\u5426\u8fd8\u80fd\u901a\u8fc7\u7f29\u7a84\u6bcf-expert \u5bbd\u5ea6\u7ee7\u7eed\u5de6\u79fb\u5230\u7ea6 0.24x\u3002",
